## Strategic Rationale

### Why 1-2 Concepts vs. 5?
- **Quality over quantity:** Professional presentation requires 16-20 hours per concept
- **Stakeholder decision:** They choose between 2 strong options vs. 5 weak ones
- **Phase 2 efficiency:** Higher-quality starting point enables faster refinement
- **Cost/time realistic:** Achievable in 2-day design sprint (Feb 1-3)

### Why These Standards?
- **Grant applications:** External reviewers expect professional execution
- **Corporate partnerships:** Need credibility in tech/ed space
- **Launch readiness:** Website/social media need production-quality assets day one
- **Brand credibility:** Polished execution signals organizational excellence

